<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Premium Subscription Expiring Soon</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .header {
            background-color: #FF9800;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
        }

        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Subscription Expiring Soon</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear {{name}},</p>
            <p>This is a reminder that your premium subscription for <strong>{{planName}}</strong> will expire on
                <strong>{{expiryDate}}</strong>.</p>

            <p>To avoid any interruption to your premium benefits, please renew your subscription before it expires.</p>

            <p style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="{{renewUrl}}" class="cta-button">Renew Subscription</a>
            </p>

            <p>If you have already renewed, please ignore this message.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>